title: Tutorial 4
text:
dt <- penguins

 plot <- dt %>%
   ggplot(aes(x=bill_length_mm, y=body_mass_g, color = sex)) +
   geom_point() +
   facet_wrap(~species, ncol= 5)+
   theme_minimal()
